OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FAnyone not yet registered to vote in
OL,7,Fthe elections taking place in England,
OL,8,FScotland and Wales on May 7 has only a
OL,9,Ffew hours left to apply.
OL,11,FThe deadline to register is 11.59 pm
OL,12,Fon Monday.
OL,14,FApplications can be submitted online
OL,15,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
