OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FElections are being held on May 7 to
OL,7,Felect members of the Scottish
OL,8,FParliament and the Senedd in Wales,
OL,9,Fwhile some 5,013 council seats in
OL,10,FEngland are up for grabs across 136
OL,11,Flocal authorities.
OL,13,FThere are also contests to choose six
OL,14,Flocal mayors.
OL,16,FMembers of the Scottish Parliament and
OL,17,Fthe Senedd were last elected in 2021,
OL,18,Fwhile this is the largest set of local
OL,19,Felections in England for three years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
