CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776731804
OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FSome 42,827 applications to register
OL,7,Fto vote were submitted on Sunday April
OL,8,F19, the highest on a single day so far
OL,9,Fthis year, government figures show.
OL,11,FAn average of 33,218 applications were
OL,12,Fmade per day in the week to April 19,
OL,13,Fup from 23,255 the previous week and
OL,14,F21,426 a fortnight ago.
OL,16,FThe contests on May 7 represent a
OL,17,Fcrucial test at the ballot box for all
OL,18,Fpolitical parties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
