OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FElections for devolved parliaments,
OL,7,Fcouncils and mayors can reflect
OL,8,Fvoters' attitudes about their local
OL,9,Farea, such as when bins are collected,
OL,10,Fthe state of parks and pavements, or
OL,11,Fthe quality of schools and hospitals.
OL,13,FBut they can also be a verdict on how
OL,14,Fparties and leaders are handling
OL,15,Fnational issues, which this year could
OL,16,Fmean the cost of living, the economy
OL,17,Fand immigration, or even foreign
OL,18,Faffairs such as the wars in Iran and
OL,19,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
