OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FNiki Nixon, director of communications
OL,7,Fand external affairs at the Electoral
OL,8,FCommission, said: "Today is your final
OL,9,Fchance to register to vote for the
OL,10,Flocal elections in England on May 7.
OL,12,F"The deadline is midnight tonight, and
OL,13,Fif you've moved home or changed your
OL,14,Fdetails in the past year, you'll need
OL,15,Fto register again.
OL,17,F"It only takes five minutes, and you
OL,18,Fcan do it online at www.gov.uk/
OL,19,Fregister-to-vote."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
