OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FRhydian Thomas, head of the Electoral
OL,7,FCommission in Wales, added: "Time is
OL,8,Frunning out to register in time for
OL,9,Fthe Senedd election on May 7.
OL,11,F"If this is your first time voting, or
OL,12,Fif your details have changed since you
OL,13,Flast voted, make sure you register by
OL,14,Fmidnight.
OL,16,F"The Senedd has powers to make laws
OL,17,Ffor Wales on a range of areas
OL,18,Fincluding transport, healthcare,
OL,19,Fhousing, education, and the economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
