PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776731804
OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,F"Those who do not register to vote in
OL,7,Ftime will miss their opportunity to
OL,8,Fmake their voices heard on the issues
OL,9,Fthat impact their daily lives."
OL,11,FIn Wales, the electoral system has
OL,12,Fchanged for the first time since it
OL,13,Fwas originally brought in.
OL,15,FThe number of seats being elected is
OL,16,Frising from 60 to 96, whilst the
OL,17,Fnumber of constituencies are falling
OL,18,Ffrom 40 to 16.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
