OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAlong with Monday's deadline to
OL,12,Fregister to vote, there are a number
OL,13,Fof other key dates before polling day.
OL,15,FThe deadline to apply for a postal
OL,16,Fvote for the elections is 5 pm on
OL,17,FTuesday, April 21.
OL,19,FApplications can be made online at
OL,20,Fgov.uk/apply-postal-vote
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
