OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FAll voters in England intending to
OL,7,Fcast a ballot in the elections on May
OL,8,F7 will not only need to be registered
OL,9,Fbut also show a form of photo
OL,10,Fidentification at the polling station.
OL,12,FNot all types of photo ID will be
OL,13,Faccepted, but a passport, driving
OL,14,Flicence or blue badge are valid.
OL,16,FAnyone without the correct
OL,17,Fidentification will need to apply for
OL,18,Fa voter authority certificate by 5 pm
OL,19,Fon Tuesday April 28, which can be done
OL,20,Fonline at gov.uk/apply-for-photo-id-
OL,21,Fvoter-authority-certificate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
