CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1776731804
OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FPhoto ID is not needed to vote in the
OL,7,Felections for the Scottish Parliament
OL,8,For Senedd.
OL,10,FApril 28 is also the deadline to apply
OL,11,Ffor a proxy vote, to allow someone to
OL,12,Fvote at a polling station on your
OL,13,Fbehalf.
OL,15,FApplications can be made online at
OL,16,Fgov.uk/apply-proxy-vote.
OL,18,FOn election day, Thursday, May 7,
OL,19,Fpolling stations will be open from 7
OL,20,Fam to 10 pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
