OL,3,CDeadline day to register to vote in
OL,4,CMay 7 elections
OL,6,FAround a third of councils in England
OL,7,Fare due to declare results overnight.
OL,9,FResults for the Scottish Parliament,
OL,10,Fthe Senedd, and most councils in
OL,11,FEngland will be declared during the
OL,12,Ffollowing day, Friday May 8.
OL,14,FFinal results from four councils will
OL,15,Fbe declared on Saturday May 9.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
